            <title>[LU-4196] Build Support for OFED 3.5 for SLES 11 SP3</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-4196</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Similar to &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3389&quot; title=&quot;Lustre b2_1 build failed on RHEL6.4 with OFA IB stack&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-3389&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-3389&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; (&lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/6448/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/#/c/6448/&lt;/a&gt;)  DCONFIG_COMMPAT_SLES_11_SP3 is needed in EXTRA_LNET_INCLUDE to build against OFED 3.5.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ll be submitting a patch for this.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
